title: Rowan Quantumstrike!
description: Cat and Dan are back to cover the highlights from the last week of cricket. Topics include: What can cricket learn from the women's football World Cup? A look ahead to the thrills that await us in the men's ODI World Cup An update on The Hundred and standout player, Rowan Quantumstrike! Plus, another thrilling Muller Award Sign up to Dan's substack for post-Ashes content over at newsletter.liebcricket.com Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
author: Dan Liebke, Cat Jones
